title: KITCH
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has quite a few vegan choices or ones that can be made vegan and are marked by VGN. Serves breakfast all day with some vegan choices. Lunch starts at 12pm. Juices, smoothies, coffee and tea are available. Supports local suppliers when possible. All items are made-in-house and made-to-order, plus are free from refined sugars, refined flours and processed foods.
